a | publisher = The Chronicle | date = 5 January 2012 | accessdate = 11 December 2014 }}</ref><ref name=\"Depleted Warriors hit the road\">{{Cite web | url = http://www.herald.co.zw/depleted-warriors-hit-the-road/ | title = Depleted Warriors hit the road | publisher = The Herald | date = 5 January 2012 | accessdate = 11 December 2014 }}</ref> The games finished a 0\u20130 draw, with Whitby coming on as a substitute.<ref name=\"Players impress Mapeza\">{{Cite web | url = http://www.chronicle.co.zw/players-impress-mapeza/ | title = Players impress Mapeza | publisher = The Chronicle | date = 9 January 2012 | accessdate = 11 December 2014 }}</ref>\n\n==Personal life==\nWhitby spent time in [[Thanet District|Thanet]], [[Kent]] as a child and has a British [[passport]].<ref name=\"Margate history\" />\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n*{{NFT player|pid=46268}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Whitby, Conrad}}\n[[Category:1984 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean footballers]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwe international footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in England]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Botswana]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriates in Botswana]]\n[[Category:Expatriate soccer players in South Africa]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean expatriates in South Africa]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:National League (English football) players]]\n[[Category:Southern Football League players]]\n[[Category:Margate F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Ramsgate F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Almondsbury F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Mangotsfield United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Keynsham Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Motor Action F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Eagles F.C. (Zimbabwe) players]]\n[[Category:Kiglon F.C. players]]\n[[Category:CAPS United players]]\n[[Category:Township Rollers F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Polokwane City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:F.C. Cape Town players]]\n[[Category:Wivenhoe Town F.C. players]]\n